{"lemma":"تَرْجَمَةُ","slug":"تَرْجَمَةُ","root":"ت.ر.ج.م","root_slug":"ت-ر-ج-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ت-ر-ج-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14983","n3860","n3859"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%AC%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of تَرْجَمَ (tarjama) (form Iq)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"translation","examples":[{"text":"التَّرْجَمَة السَّبْعِينِيَّة","english":"the Septuagint"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"interpretation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"biography"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"introduction, preface, foreword"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"subtitle (“textual versions of the dialog in films”)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See the root ت ر ج م (t r j m) for more.\nCompare Classical Syriac ܬܘܪܓܡܐ (turgāmā), Hebrew תַּרְגּוּם (targúm), Amharic ትርጉም (tərgum)."},"ipa":["/tar.d͡ʒa.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14983","headword_ar":"تَرْجَمَةٌ","root":"rjm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraAjimu","text_ar":"تَرَاجِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trjm","text_ar":"ترجم"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3860","headword_ar":"تَرْجَمَةٌ","root":"trjm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of the verb above: used as a simple subst.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An interpretation: a translation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taraAjimu","text_ar":"تَرَاجِمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A life,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"biography,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"biographical notice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any person: pl. as above. (TA, passim; and other works of post-classical times.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An article, a head, chapter, section,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"paragraph,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a book. (TA, passim; and other works of post-classical times.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n3859","headword_ar":"تَرْجَمَهُ","root":"trjm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjm","text_ar":"رجم"},{"kind":"text","text":", and Msb and K in the present art.,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarojama Eanohu","text_ar":"تَرْجَمَ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarojamapN","text_ar":"تَرْجَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (KL,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He interpreted it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, KL, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"explained it in another language;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, KL;) namely, the speech, or language, (S, Msb, K,) of another person: (Msb:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"translated it from one language into another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he explained it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, his own speech. (Msb.) [This verb is essentially the same in Arabic, Chaldee, and Ethiopic.] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarojamahu","text_ar":"تَرْجَمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wrote his life; wrote a biography,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"biographical notice, of him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, passim; and other works of post-classical times.) ―         -b3-  Accord. to the K, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this verb is a radical: but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tarojumaAnN","text_ar":"تَرْجُمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","KL","S","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}